NG0200:2: yongs su rdzogs dang bye brag la //
NG0200:3: gsang sngags gang bsgrub 'di skabs sbyar //
NG0200:5: dper na nor bu+u rin chen 'dra //
NG0200:8: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las //
NG0200:9: bsad mnan rlung 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi le'u ste so
NG0200:10: brgyad pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus pa'i 'khor
NG0200:11: rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun tu bzang
NG0200:12: po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol pa
NG0200:14: thams cad ston pa kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:15: thugs rje che mchog he ru ka / 'jig rten ye shes gang bsgrubs kyang *//
NG0200:16: srog gzer kha bsgyur rim pa gang *//
NG0200:17: de skad ces gsol bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:18: ye shes 'jig rten gang bsgrubs kyang *//
NG0200:19: srog sdom gzer bzhis ma thebs na //
NG0200:20: nam yang don med yug pas kyang *//
NG0200:22: yongs rdzogs dpal gyi srog 'phrog thabs //
NG0200:23: gcig shes pas ni kun srog thob //
NG0200:24: dper na sgra gcan 'dzin gyis khas //
NG0200:25: nam mkha'i nyi ma gcig zin pas //
NG0200:26: chu bran stong gi nyi ma kun //
NG0200:27: ma bzung bar yang stong srog thob //
NG0200:28: de phyir srog gi gzer bzhi gces //
NG0200:29: dben pa'i gnas su man+dal bsham //
NG0200:30: dbus su mtshan ldan ka pa lar //
NG0200:31: dpal chen sku gcig gsal bar dgod //
NG0200:32: bskyed rdzogs gzhung bsrang 'dzab rdzogs rjes //
NG0200:33: mi rtog bya bral so mar gnas //
NG0200:34: de nas dpal gyi srog 'phrog thabs //
NG0200:35: ting 'dzin gzer dang snying po'i gzer //
NG0200:37: ting 'dzin gzer ni thod sku la //
NG0200:38: rtse gcig sems gzung yengs mi bya //
NG0200:39: yul gsum gyad du gyur pa dang *//
NG0200:40: dpa' ldan he ru dngos dang mjal //
NG0200:41: bzlog pa he ru kas mi spyod //
NG0200:43: sku ni nams kyang mthong mi 'gyur //
NG0200:44: snying po sngags gzer yongs rdzogs kyi //
NG0200:45: gtso bo'i sngags dag sel med bzlas //
NG0200:46: thugs srog hum la rtsa sngags bskor //
NG0200:48: de tshe dpal byon lung yang ston //
NG0200:49: nus pa'i rtsal rdzogs lha rnams 'khor //
NG0200:50: srog snying bsnyen rdzogs gzer med na //
NG0200:51: lha dang dam can 'khor mi srid //
NG0200:52: dgongs pa'i gzer ni zhi khro'i lha //
NG0200:53: yongs rdzogs dpal chen rang sems las //
NG0200:54: gud na med cing ru dra yang *//
NG0200:55: logs na med do rang gi sems //
NG0200:56: sems nyid stong pa chos kyi sku //
NG0200:57: gsal la ma 'gags longs spyod rdzogs //
NG0200:58: sna tshogs rang shar sprul pa'i sku //
NG0200:59: snang ba yab la stong pa yum //
NG0200:60: snang stong dbyer med ye shes sku //
NG0200:61: 'gyu dran rnam rtog bsam yas kyang *//
NG0200:62: yongs su rdzogs pa dpal gyi 'khor //
NG0200:63: bsam gyis mi khyab ye sangs rgyas //
NG0200:66: dgongs pa mi 'gyur gzer med na //
NG0200:67: dpal chen grub kyang thun mong las //
NG0200:68: mchog mi 'grub cing ru drar gol //
NG0200:72: sems kyi nus pa rtsal rdzogs te //
NG0200:73: gang ltar bsam pa de ltar snang *//
NG0200:74: sngags dang phyag rgya'i byin rlabs mthus //
NG0200:75: zhi rgyas dbang drag mngon spyod sogs //
NG0200:76: phan gnod las ka gang yang 'grub //
NG0200:77: dper na nor bu gcig nyid la //
NG0200:78: gsol mchod rkyen gyis bye brag tu //
NG0200:79: ji ltar 'dod pa so sor bskang *//
NG0200:81: dmigs gtad gcig la don mi 'grub //
NG0200:83: the'u rang tha chung gcig kyang gis //
NG0200:84: phrin las thogs med las kun 'grub //
NG0200:85: thams cad sems kyi cho 'phrul yin //
NG0200:86: kha bsgyur gnad kyi man ngag 'di //
NG0200:87: yongs rdzogs dpal chen he ru nas //
NG0200:88: 'gong po grong rgyug yan chad po'i //
NG0200:89: ye shes 'jig rten gang na yang *//
NG0200:90: gcig la bsnyen rdzogs grub thob na //
NG0200:91: las kyi kha bsgyur gang yang 'grub //
NG0200:92: dper na lcags rdo ngar btul na //
NG0200:93: go khrab mtshon cha cir bsgyur nyan //
NG0200:94: rdo ma thul ba lcags yin kyang *//
NG0200:95: ma bsgyur dngos kyi bzo mi btub //
NG0200:96: de phyir lha 'dre gcig bsgrub na //
NG0200:97: kha sgyur gang la zhugs kyang grub //
NG0200:98: dang po tshe sring kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:99: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:100: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:101: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:102: khyad par b+han+d+ha mtshan ldan du //
NG0200:103: tshe chang tshe mar ri lu blug / kha ni tshe zan zlum pos bcad //
NG0200:104: de la gzungs thag btags byas la //
NG0200:105: yongs rdzogs rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:106: tshe yi yang snying 'di sbrel bzlas //
NG0200:107: a yuhpha la sid+d+hi hum a /
NG0200:108: rtags ni khol dang lud pa 'byung *//
NG0200:109: de ltar byung na tshe bstim la //
NG0200:110: tshe 'brang za zhing tshe chang btung *//
NG0200:112: rmongs po srid spel kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:113: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:114: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:115: 'di nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:116: khyad par srin rdo khab len dang *//
NG0200:117: bud med mngal khrag bye ru dang *//
NG0200:118: de rnams le brgan dar du gril //
NG0200:119: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de dang *//
NG0200:120: srid spel yang snying 'di sbrel bzlas //
NG0200:121: pu tra a yuhpha la sid+d+hi hum /
NG0200:122: ra lug gang shi'i gta' ru gzhug / mchod bstod gsol la rab brtson bya //
NG0200:123: bud med lnga bcu lon gyur kyang *//
NG0200:125: dbul sel nor bsgrub kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:126: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:127: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:128: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:129: khyad par rin chen ga'u ru //
NG0200:130: gser dngul zangs lcags sna lnga blug / nor lhar gyur tshad gzungs sngags @#//
NG0200:132: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:133: nor sgrub yang snying 'di sbrel bzlas //
NG0200:134: rat+na pha la sid+d+hi b+h+rum nan kha d+he push+tim sid+d+hi hum /
NG0200:135: zas nor gang 'dod gsol ba gdab //
NG0200:136: longs spyod phun sum tshogs par 'gyur //
NG0200:137: mig mthong mngon shes kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:138: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:139: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:140: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:141: khyad par 'ug pa smug po'i mig / byi la'i mig dang lung thang dang *//
NG0200:142: de rnams ra dkar 'o mas sbru //
NG0200:143: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de dang *//
NG0200:144: rno mthong rtsa ba'i sngags sbrel bzlas //
NG0200:145: omhma d+ha ma d+ha la tsak+shu tsak+shu pra be sha phat /
NG0200:146: rdzas de mig la byugs pa na //
NG0200:147: srid pa gsum yang mthong bar 'gyur //
NG0200:149: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:150: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:151: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:152: khyad par gtor tshogs bzang po bsham //
NG0200:153: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:155: 'byung po 'dul byed sha trum tsu lu tsu lu phat phat /
NG0200:156: chos skyong bskul zhing dbang yang gzug / phur thun sngags kyis brab pa na //
NG0200:157: gnod byed skad ngan tser tser 'ong *//
NG0200:158: mna' bsgag 'gags bsdam rjes gcod bya //
NG0200:160: ser ba srung ba'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:161: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:162: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:163: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:164: khyad par zas gtor phyir mchod de //
NG0200:165: bden pa bsgo rjes mtho skor bya //
NG0200:166: de nas ser rkang nam shar tshe //
NG0200:167: bdag nyid yongs rdzogs dpal chen bskyed //
NG0200:168: dregs pa thams cad bka' nyan bsam //
NG0200:169: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:170: ser srung yang snying 'di sbrel bzlas //
NG0200:171: yo ger yor ge yang sad ram ram sad phur phura'ur 'ur yang sad //
NG0200:172: thal chen nyung dkar dag la bsngags //
NG0200:173: gdong du gtor na bzlog par 'gyur //
NG0200:174: dkor nor srung ba'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:175: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:176: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:177: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:178: khyad par nor rdzas yul khams rnams //
NG0200:179: ming gzugs lha yi rten la bcing *//
NG0200:180: kho la nor rdzas bsrung ma bcol //
NG0200:181: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:182: nor srung sngags 'di sbrel la bzlas //
NG0200:184: rat+na ra sti nor srungs shig / de byas nor de gzhan khyer na //
NG0200:186: skabs skabs gsol ka bcol gtad bya //
NG0200:187: rang gis stong tshe zhu gsol bya //
NG0200:189: sbyor ba nag po'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:190: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:191: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:192: 'di nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:193: khyad par sngags 'dis rgyun tu bsrung *//
NG0200:197: om b+hi sha g+ho li ra mi ya u be swa ha /
NG0200:198: yang na nyer re nang re bzlas //
NG0200:199: des ni bdag srung rgyal por 'gyur //
NG0200:200: 'on te byung zin gzhan bsrung na //
NG0200:201: sngags 'di chu la mang bzlas blud //
NG0200:204: ka ma ra tri ye swa ha /
NG0200:205: gang la dogs pa'i zas kun la //
NG0200:207: mtshon cha srung ba'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:208: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:209: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:210: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:211: khyad par sngags 'di btags pas bsrung *//
NG0200:212: yang snying rgyun bsnyen spyi gtsug gdags //
NG0200:213: mtshon kha snyol byed yi ge khrom //
NG0200:214: mthing shog dag la gser gyis bris //
NG0200:215: dar sna lngas gril rab gnas bya //
NG0200:216: de 'dra gsum byas spyi gtsug dang *//
NG0200:217: mgrin pa snying gar gdags par bya //
NG0200:218: om rno sod bzlog chum dril swa ha /
NG0200:219: sa la nyer gcig sngags byas te //
NG0200:220: nam dgos dus su gtor bas grub //
NG0200:221: ngag gnon sgrol ba'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:222: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:223: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:224: de nyid gzhug bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:225: khyad par mtshan ldan thod pa'i nang *//
NG0200:226: chang dang a mr-i ta sbyar te //
NG0200:227: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:229: a shig shig phyung phyung khrol khrol swa ha /
NG0200:230: brgya dang rtsa brgyad rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0200:231: de nyid bdud rtsi lce rdo rjer //
NG0200:232: bsam te thigs pa lan gsum gzhag / de yang spyi gtsug mgrin pa dang *//
NG0200:233: snying ga rnams su gsum gsum gzhag / sgo gsum bcings pa kun grol bsam //
NG0200:234: mnan gtad ngag mnan kun grol 'gyur //
NG0200:235: pra phab pa yi kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:236: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:237: de la bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:238: de yi gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:239: khyad par 'phying dkar ras dkar steng *//
NG0200:240: nas kyi g.yung drung bris byas nas //
NG0200:241: pra rten khye'u bu mor rung *//
NG0200:242: yul chos ma gos gtsang ma bzhag / srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:243: pra dbab sngags 'di sbrel la bzlas //
NG0200:244: mu shri ku shri pra ma da na ti b+ha
NG0200:245: ga sid+d+hi g+har khug / nga'i bu mo dgar chug
NG0200:246: kho'i bu mo smyor chug / nas la bsngags te
NG0200:247: pra rten gzir / legs nyes gang dris smra bar
NG0200:248: 'gyur // mdze nad gso ba'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:249: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:250: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:251: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:252: chos skyong bskang zhing phrin las bcol //
NG0200:253: 'brub khung nang du sbal pa'i gzugs //
NG0200:254: gang gnod sa la byas te gzhug / lus po
NG0200:255: tshon skud dra bar gzhug / sug bzhi phur pas
NG0200:256: stod la gzir // srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags nyid dang *//
NG0200:257: sde brgyad gnad sngags 'di yis gzir //
NG0200:258: na ga ra dza sa ma @#//
NG0200:259: ya snying la khrag du rmugs /
NG0200:261: na ga rak+sha rak+sha ma ra ya rbad rbad //
NG0200:262: zhag grangs nyer gcig thun gyis brab //
NG0200:263: sbal pa skad ngan tser tser yong *//
NG0200:264: mdze nad mi bzad sos par 'gyur //
NG0200:265: dgra bo gsod pa'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:266: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:267: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:268: 'di nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:269: khyad par nyung dkar nyung nag dang *//
NG0200:270: zangs lcags rdo yi phye ma dang *//
NG0200:271: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de dang *//
NG0200:272: gsod pa'i sngags rgod 'di sprel bzlas //
NG0200:273: che ge mo sha trum a mu kam / srog
NG0200:274: rtsa dmar po hur thum ma ra ya rbad rbad
NG0200:275: // mdor na las kun rtse gcig ste //
NG0200:276: 'di yang zhag grangs nyer gcig bsgrub //
NG0200:278: ser ba 'bebs pa'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:279: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:280: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:281: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:282: khyad par nyung dkar gu gul dang *//
NG0200:283: khrag sna tshogs tshad gtsod khrag la //
NG0200:284: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:285: ser ba'i yang snying 'di sbrel bzlas //
NG0200:286: khrom khrom hril hril shar shar phob phob //
NG0200:287: gnam mi mthong bar nyer gcig bsgrub //
NG0200:288: thebs dus mthun de dgra yul gtor //
NG0200:290: gnam lcags thog 'bebs kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:291: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:292: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:293: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:294: khyad par gser dngul thig po dang *//
NG0200:295: thog mded nyung dkar thun la bya //
NG0200:296: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de dang *//
NG0200:297: thog gi drag sngags 'di sbrel bzlas //
NG0200:298: ram ram hril hril phrom phrom shar shar phob phob //
NG0200:299: nyer gcig bsgrubs te thun rgod ni //
NG0200:300: dgra bo'i khang pa dag la gtor //
NG0200:302: gtad khram gzhug pa'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:303: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:304: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:305: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:306: khyad par gro ga shog shog la //
NG0200:307: ling+ga ming rus ldan bris la //
NG0200:308: tha ma sbrul nag 'khyil pas bskor //
NG0200:309: zhi ba ra'am sbal par gzhug / drag po mdze thod rkang du brub //
NG0200:310: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de dang *//
NG0200:311: klu yi drag sngags 'di sbrel bzlas //
NG0200:312: na ga ra dza sa ma ya khug sprig sprig nr-i dza /
NG0200:313: na ga shig srog rtsa chod sa ma ya /
NG0200:315: skye tshe shang tshe la bsngags brab //
NG0200:316: las la sbyar ba'i thal bar bcas //
NG0200:317: la chas kha bsdam gting rdo gdags //
NG0200:318: byang bltas chu mig sngo mtshams gtad //
NG0200:320: ltas ngan cho 'phrul kha sgyur ni //

NG0200:322: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:323: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:324: khyad par wa spyang dom dred dang *//
NG0200:327: ltas ngan snying khrag sna tshogs dang *//
NG0200:328: nyung dkar nyung nag thun rdzas la //
NG0200:329: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de dang *//
NG0200:330: ltas ngan sngags 'di sbrel la bzlas //
NG0200:331: li phrim ram kar rma ri //
NG0200:336: rdzas rnams phyogs sam khang par bskyal //
NG0200:338: ngan thabs sel nag kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:339: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:340: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:341: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:342: khyad par khyi phag spyang thod dang *//
NG0200:343: sha zan bya yi mchu sder dang *//
NG0200:344: rabs chad nag po'i thod pa la //
NG0200:345: drag po'i ming rus yul mkhar dang *//
NG0200:346: nor rdzas che bran thams cad brub //
NG0200:347: srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:349: tsakra rak+sha tshal pa kyi khyer /
NG0200:350: rtsad chod drung phyung rmang nas shig / ste shog ya //
NG0200:351: rdzas rnams dril te dgra bo yi //
NG0200:352: khang sa zhing sa dur sar sba //
NG0200:353: mkhar 'gyel zhing skam dur rnams 'khrug / dgra rnams phung zhing brlag par 'gyur //
NG0200:354: seng ge kha 'thab kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:355: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:356: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:357: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:358: khyad par 'dag pa'i seng ge gnyis //
NG0200:359: khong stong byas la so btang la //

NG0200:361: lha dang srung ma'i ming gzugs rnams //
NG0200:362: dpa' brjid dmag 'dren tshul du brub //
NG0200:363: srog sngags bsnyen bsgrub las dril gzhug / nag po'i nang du kho yi ni //
NG0200:364: lha srung sngags ming gzugs bcas bris //
NG0200:365: sde brgyad dag gi ming byang bri //
NG0200:366: de gnyis kha 'thab bar du ni //
NG0200:367: ban d+he kho yi ling+ga gzhug / srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la /
NG0200:368: seng ge kha 'thab rgyal sngags bzlas //
NG0200:369: nr-i ma ra ya ni nr-i hur thum //

NG0200:372: zangs lcags nyung dkar nyung nag la //
NG0200:373: bsngags shing ling+ga de la brdeg / zla drug lon tshe de 'chi 'gyur //
NG0200:374: rbod gtong zlog pa'i kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:375: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:376: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:377: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:378: khyad par kho yi rkang rjes dang *//
NG0200:379: dri ma dag la ling+ga bya //
NG0200:380: ming rus bris la snying gar glan //
NG0200:381: mchog phur sor brgyad snying gar gdab //
NG0200:382: rang gi mal 'og gru gsum nang *//
NG0200:383: nya bo dug khrag byugs la bzhag / dong kha rgya gram g.yam pas bcad //
NG0200:384: de steng rang nyid lhar gsal 'dug / srog snying rtsa ba'i sngags de la //
NG0200:385: bod gtong zlog sngags 'di sbrel bzlas //

NG0200:388: brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas la gcig thub //
NG0200:391: khri tsho gcig gis rtag tu thub //
NG0200:392: sbod gtong thams cad des bzlog 'gyur //
NG0200:393: mu stegs ngag gnon kha sgyur ni //
NG0200:394: ye shes 'jig rten gang yang rung *//
NG0200:395: de yi bsnyen bsgrub yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:396: de nyid gzhung bsrang mthun rdzas bsham //
NG0200:397: khyad par kho yi chu rjes la //
NG0200:398: chu la 'bogs pa'i rjes sa la //
NG0200:399: kho yi gzugs ni kha bde bya //
NG0200:400: shog shog lce dpyang og mar drang *//
